step-certctl (0.1.2) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix: remove invalid --key flag from step ca renew (caused "too many
    positional arguments" with step-cli 0.28.7)
  * Docs: document pmxcfs permission limits for Proxmox pveproxy configs
  * Docs: add troubleshooting for mTLS renewal failure due to missing
    clientAuth in CA provisioner template

 -- Mohamed Reda Elkhadiri <mohamed@elkhadiri.com>  Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

step-certctl (0.1.1) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix: accept days suffix (e.g. 4d) in EXPIRES_IN by converting to hours
  * Docs: clarify EXPIRES_IN accepts hours (8h, 24h) or days (1d, 7d)

 -- Mohamed Reda Elkhadiri <mohamed@elkhadiri.com>  Tue, 10 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

step-certctl (0.1.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * Support for certificate issuance and renewal
  * Config-driven approach with per-certificate config files
  * Systemd timer-based automatic renewal
  * Public key comparison to avoid unnecessary service reloads
  * Support for custom ownership, permissions, and reload commands
  * Example configs for Proxmox, nginx, HAProxy, and custom apps

 -- Mohamed Reda Elkhadiri <mohamed@elkhadiri.com>  Sun, 09 Mar 2026 21:00:00 +0000
